data.description: PRIVACY is paramount at "Casa del Alba" (house of sunrise). Named by the current owners for the fabulous sunrises! 113 Lucerne Place is situated at the end of a PAVED road on 2.48 gorgeous acres offering incredible seasonal MOUNTAIN VIEWS. As you enter the home through the cozy "farmhouse" inspired all-weather room you are led through the front door and into the beautifully customized kitchen. This kitchen boasts a large functional island, abundant solid surface counter space, built-in coffee/tea bar, and a pantry hidden behind a sliding barn door. You will love the open concept floorplan that features vaulted and beamed ceilings and draws your attention to the inviting stone fireplace in the great room. Off of the great room is another massive living space, full of windows that could be used for a large dining room, media room or any flex space you may want/need. The spectacular master suite on the main level offers dual closets and loads of space. Just off of the master is bonus room that leads you out to the deck and would make a great office, gym or sitting room. There is a lovely guest room on this main level along with a nice sized laundry room. Up the stairs you come to an open loft space and then the 3rd bedroom and 2nd full bathroom. Additional attic storage space is available on this level too. There is 600 sq. ft of unfinished space in the basement that makes a great workshop area. Additionally, there is a detached outbuilding that is perfect for even more storage! This property offers plenty of parking space for you, your family and your guests as well as FIBER internet. You will fall in love with the gorgeous views, stunning sunrises, and the sounds of pure nature surrounding you here! If you decide to make this your home, you will be just minutes to wineries, Helen, Cleveland, fly fishing, hiking, and all of what the North Georgia Mountains have to offer.
